data.description: Looking for your mountain home? Come see this adorable 3 bed 2 bath located just off of the 260 and Porter Mountain Rd in a quiet neighborhood. This home is all ready for winter with a brand new roof just installed for you, a freshly painted interior and exterior, and newer windows! There is a gated fenced in side yard with room for toys, pets, and it even has a large drive in gate. Huge cement slab in the back yard could be used for parking, gatherings, or build a workshop! Inside the home you will be welcomed by a built in entertainment center and a fireplace with a woodstove insert for those chilly nights. Beautiful upgraded plantation shutters allow for plenty of warm natural light during the day and privacy at night. This is a split floor plan with nice sized bedrooms and closets. This would be a great starter home, vacation home, or income property. Lots of possibilities with this one! Schedule your showing today! The home has some un-level spots throughout, it has been evaluated by a structural engineer, and deemed as structurally sound. Please see attached Foundation Report.
